     Folgende Fehler können vorkommen:
	- Mirth Error weil falscher Barcode gescannt wurde, als FID erscheint die KSN (CSN) Nummer beginnend mit KSN. (im Moment wird ein txt file auf ksl-vw2k530 geführt um diese Fehler zu tracken)
	  Die FID's zu den KSN Nummern bei Pedro nachfragen, Messages mit FID anstatt KSN nachversenden.
	- Mirth Error weil falscher Barcode gescannt wurde, als FID erscheint die <ok> weil das System übersteuert wurde. Es kann nichts gemacht werden, Fehler auf Schnittstelle löschen.

     Der Channel liest eine *.hl7 Datei von einer SMB-Freigabe.
     Source-Transformer:
          OBX.5.1 wird als Dateiname verstanden. Das File dieses Names wird von einer SMB-Freigabe gelesen und als Attachment gespeichert.
          So erscheint es nur 1-mal in der Datenbank. Gibt es Probleme beim Lesen des Files, wird die Nachricht auf Status "FILTERED" gesetzt.
     Destination PDF:
          Das PDF-File wird auf eine SMB-Freigabe geschrieben, wobei optional gefiltert werden kann

80-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.name: SrvLog_MirOsm_PR_LU_Xml_10_90080_DbRdr
80-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.file:
SELECT 
	E.ID AS EVENT_ID,
	E.DATE_CREATED AS EVENT_DATE_CREATED,
	E.NAME AS EVENT_NAME, 
	E.EVENT_LEVEL AS EVENT_EVENT_LEVEL, 
	E.OUTCOME AS EVENT_OUTCOME, 
	E.ATTRIBUTES AS EVENT_ATTRIBUTES, 
	E.USER_ID AS EVENT_USER_ID, 
	E.IP_ADDRESS AS EVENT_IP_ADDRESS, 
	E.SERVER_ID AS EVENT_SERVER_ID,
	P.USERNAME AS PERSON_USERNAME
FROM EVENT E LEFT JOIN PERSON P ON E.USER_ID = P.ID WHERE E.SENT IS NULL AND E.NAME NOT LIKE 'Data Pruner'
80-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.description:
Beschreibung:
     Sendet events aus der Mirth-Datenbank (Tabelle EVENT) zu SOC via Crible Server
     ( Logins, Admin-Tasks etc)
     Anstelle von Syslog wird eine TCP-Verbindung mit JSON als Datenformat verwendet

         Hanspeter Brun
     
     Destinations:
         Brian Chour, Michael Luksch

	E.ATTRIBUTES AS EVENT_ATTRIBUTES, 
	E.USER_ID AS EVENT_USER_ID, 
	E.IP_ADDRESS AS EVENT_IP_ADDRESS, 
	E.SERVER_ID AS EVENT_SERVER_ID,
	P.USERNAME AS PERSON_USERNAME
FROM EVENT E LEFT JOIN PERSON P ON E.USER_ID = P.ID WHERE E.SENT IS NULL AND E.NAME NOT LIKE 'Data Pruner'

82-c56bf050-3d58-40a6-bf57-d40d05fdd270-.name: BezLid_IdxMvw_PR_LU_Sql_10_30130_DbRdr
82-c56bf050-3d58-40a6-bf57-d40d05fdd270-.file:
/****** Skript für SmartACT Personal
MD_MDTID == 1000=Mitarbeiter, 1001=Fremdmitarbeiter, 1002=Sichtausweis
CRD_STATE == 104=Aktiv, 101=Personalisiert, 102=Pers.Bestätigt, 103=Ausgegeben, ,105=TempGesperrt,
			106=EndgültigGesperrt, 107=Vernichtet, 110=Transport   ******/
SELECT	
	T_MASTERDATA.PERSONNEL_NUMBER AS PIS_NR,
	T_MASTERDATA.LASTNAME,
	T_MASTERDATA.MAIDEN_NAME,
	T_MASTERDATA.FIRSTNAME,
	T_MASTERDATA.FORM_OF_ADDRESS AS ANREDE,
	T_MASTERDATA.TITLE,
	T_MASTERDATA.BIRTHDATE,
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_STREET,
	'' AS adr2,
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_ZIP,
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_CITY,
	T_MASTERDATA.COSTCENTRE AS KST_NR,
	T_MASTERDATA.DEPARTMENT AS KST,
	T_MASTERDATA.NATIONALITY AS STELLENBEZ, 
	T_MASTERDATA.PASSPORTNUMBER AS TAETIGKEIT,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE1 AS EINTRITTSDATUM,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE2 AS AUSTRITTSDATUM,
	T_CARD.CRD_STATE,
	T_MASTERDATA.ID_CARD_NUMBER AS KGHCID,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT1 AS UIDPRIME,
	T_MASTERDATA.ID_CARD_NUMBER AS CID,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT2 AS UIDADVANT,
	T_MASTERDATA.BUILDING AS PARKPROFIL,
	T_MASTERDATA.PHONE AS ORGEH,
	T_MASTERDATA.PLACE_OF_BIRTH as STELL

	
FROM         T_MASTERDATA LEFT OUTER JOIN
                      T_CARD ON T_MASTERDATA. PERSONNEL_NUMBER = T_CARD.PERSONNEL_NUMBER
where CRD_STATE = 104 and MD_MDTID = 1000
82-c56bf050-3d58-40a6-bf57-d40d05fdd270-.description:

MD_MDTID == 1000=Mitarbeiter, 1001=Fremdmitarbeiter, 1002=Sichtausweis

			106=EndgültigGesperrt, 107=Vernichtet, 110=Transport   ******/
SELECT

	T_MASTERDATA.FORM_OF_ADDRESS AS ANREDE,
	T_MASTERDATA.TITLE,

	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_STREET,
	'' AS adr2,
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_ZIP,
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_CITY,
	T_MASTERDATA.COSTCENTRE AS KST_NR,
	T_MASTERDATA.DEPARTMENT AS KST,
	T_MASTERDATA.NATIONALITY AS STELLENBEZ, 
	T_MASTERDATA.PASSPORTNUMBER AS TAETIGKEIT,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE1 AS EINTRITTSDATUM,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE2 AS AUSTRITTSDATUM,
	T_CARD.CRD_STATE,
	T_MASTERDATA.ID_CARD_NUMBER AS KGHCID,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT1 AS UIDPRIME,
	T_MASTERDATA.ID_CARD_NUMBER AS CID,
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT2 AS UIDADVANT,
	T_MASTERDATA.BUILDING AS PARKPROFIL,
	T_MASTERDATA.PHONE AS ORGEH,

82-9d5bb97b-c382-43b7-8f82-9b66552a13b8-.name: MitLid_IdxMvw_PR_LU_Xml_10_30107_DbRdr
82-9d5bb97b-c382-43b7-8f82-9b66552a13b8-.file:
/****** Skript für SmartACT Personal
MD_MDTID == 1000=Mitarbeiter, 1001=Fremdmitarbeiter, 1002=Sichtausweis
CRD_STATE == 104=Aktiv, 101=Personalisiert, 102=Pers.Bestätigt, 103=Ausgegeben, ,105=TempGesperrt,
			106=EndgültigGesperrt, 107=Vernichtet, 110=Transport******/
SELECT	T_MASTERDATA.MD_ID, T_MASTERDATA.MD_MDTID, 
	T_MASTERDATA.PERSONNEL_NUMBER AS PIS_NR, T_MASTERDATA.ID_CARD_NUMBER AS KGHCID, 
	T_MASTERDATA.FORM_OF_ADDRESS AS ANREDE, T_MASTERDATA.TITLE, 
	T_MASTERDATA.LASTNAME, T_MASTERDATA.FIRSTNAME, 
	T_MASTERDATA.MAIDEN_NAME, T_MASTERDATA.BIRTHDATE, 
	T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_STREET, T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_ZIP, T_MASTERDATA.OFFICE_ADR_CITY, 
	T_MASTERDATA.DEPARTMENT AS KST, T_MASTERDATA.COSTCENTRE AS KST_NR, 
	T_MASTERDATA.NATIONALITY AS STELLENBEZ, T_MASTERDATA.PASSPORTNUMBER AS TAETIGKEIT, 
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT1 AS UIDPRIME, T_MASTERDATA.INFOTEXT2 AS UIDADVANT, 
	T_MASTERDATA.INFOBIGTEXT1 AS BEZ_2, T_MASTERDATA.INFOBIGTEXT2 AS BEZ_3, 
	T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE1 AS EINTRITTSDATUM, T_MASTERDATA.INFODATE2 AS AUSTRITTSDATUM, 
	T_MASTERDATA.BUILDING AS PARKPROFIL, T_MASTERDATA.PHONE AS ORGEH,
	T_CARD.CRD_ID, T_CARD.CRD_STATE, T_CARD.CRD_CTID,
	T_CARD.LASTNAME AS LASTNAME2, T_CARD.FIRSTNAME AS FIRSTNAME2, 
	T_CARD.INFOTEXT1 AS UIDPRIME2, T_CARD.INFOTEXT2 AS UIDADVANT2
FROM         T_MASTERDATA LEFT OUTER JOIN
                      T_CARD ON T_MASTERDATA. PERSONNEL_NUMBER = T_CARD.PERSONNEL_NUMBER
ORDER BY LASTNAME

82-b0782973-4b80-426c-b795-0b4e10f926e0-.name: NetWrk_DevExp_PR_LU_Sql_10_50108_DbRdr
82-b0782973-4b80-426c-b795-0b4e10f926e0-.file:
select resourcename,displaytype,vendorname,OSTYPE,address,series,model,columnvalue1,columnvalue2,
columnvalue3,MACADDRESS,osversion,imagefilename,serialnumber,systemdescription,systemlocation 
from NCMResource  left join Resources on NCMResource.resourceid=Resources.resourceid 
inner join NEComponent on Resources.resourceid=NEComponent.networkelementid 
inner join  NEInterface on NEComponent.resourceid=NEInterface.resourceid 
inner join IPV4Address on NEInterface.neinterfaceaddressid=IPV4Address.addressid 
left join  NCMResourceCustomColumn on NCMResource.Resourceid=NCMResourceCustomColumn.resourceid 
inner join NCMRESOURCESINFO on RESOURCES.RESOURCEID=NCMRESOURCESINFO.RESOURCEID 
inner join NCMVENDORDEVICE on NCMRESOURCESINFO.DEVICETEMPLATEID=NCMVENDORDEVICE.DEVICETEMPLATEID 
inner join NCMVENDOR on NCMVENDORDEVICE.VENDORID=NCMVENDOR.VENDORID 
inner join networkelement on networkelement.resourceid=necomponent.networkelementid 
inner join nedetails on nedetails.resourceid=networkelement.resourceid

82-12f6ca2a-07c0-4900-9c30-07756e1e7162-.name: PerTim_PepPly_PR_LU_Sql_10_30124_DbRdr
82-12f6ca2a-07c0-4900-9c30-07756e1e7162-.file:
SELECT 
	'PERSONALNUMMER' AS PERSONALNUMMER,
	'IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN' AS IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN,
	'DATUM' AS DATUM,
	'UNIQUEIDENTIFIER' AS MYUID
FROM DUAL
UNION
SELECT 
	PERSONALNUMMER AS PERSONALNUMMER,
	TO_CHAR (IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN) AS IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN,
	TO_CHAR (DATUM,'DD.MM.YYYY') AS DATUM,
	PERSONALNUMMER || '' AS MYUID
FROM MIS.V_HEATINFORMATIK
ORDER BY PERSONALNUMMER DESC

82-13a419ca-099d-4a2e-b69f-a38cef438fd5-.name: SrvInv_HeaCmd_PR_LU_Sql_10_50103_DbRdr
82-13a419ca-099d-4a2e-b69f-a38cef438fd5-.file:
SELECT	CI.Unterklasse AS untkl,
		CI.InventoryNumber AS invnr, 
		CI.DNS AS dns, 
		CI.Status AS status, 
		CI.ShortDescription AS descr, 
		CI.Monitoringstatus AS monitoring, 
		CI.MaintenanceWindow AS maintwind, 
		CI.MACAddress AS macad, 
		Employee.DisplayName AS dispname, 
		LocationGroup.RoomNumber AS raumnr
FROM		CI LEFT JOIN
		LocationGroup ON CI.DeviceLocationLink_RecID = LocationGroup.RecId LEFT JOIN
		Employee ON CI.OwnerIT_RecId = Employee.RecId
WHERE	CI.CIType = 'Zentraleinfrastruktur'  AND CI.Status != 'Retired'
ORDER BY	Unterklasse,DNS

82-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.name: SrvLog_MirOsm_PR_LU_Xml_10_90082_DbRdr
82-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.file:
SELECT 
	E.ID AS EVENT_ID,
	E.DATE_CREATED AS EVENT_DATE_CREATED,
	E.NAME AS EVENT_NAME, 
	E.EVENT_LEVEL AS EVENT_EVENT_LEVEL, 
	E.OUTCOME AS EVENT_OUTCOME, 
	E.ATTRIBUTES AS EVENT_ATTRIBUTES, 
	E.USER_ID AS EVENT_USER_ID, 
	E.IP_ADDRESS AS EVENT_IP_ADDRESS, 
	E.SERVER_ID AS EVENT_SERVER_ID,
	P.USERNAME AS PERSON_USERNAME
FROM EVENT E LEFT JOIN PERSON P ON E.USER_ID = P.ID WHERE E.SENT IS NULL AND E.NAME NOT LIKE 'Data Pruner'

Insert into MF_CUSTOM.SPARE_SYNEDRA_ARCHIV(
	PID,
	FALLID,
	DOKID_LUKS,
	IMPORTDATUM,
	DOKDATUM,
	POINTER,
	AKTENPLAN_ID,
	ERZEUGER,
	ERZEUGUNGSDATUM,
	AENDERER,
	AENDERUNGSDATUM,
	DOKSTATUS,
	AREAOFEXPERTISE,
	DOCUMENTNAME)
VALUES(
	${PATIENT_NR},
	${FALLID},
	${DOKID_LUKS},
	TO_DATE(${IMPORTDATUM}, 'DD.MM.YYYY hh24:mi:ss'),
	TO_DATE(${DOKDATUM}, 'DD.MM.YYYY hh24:mi:ss'),
	${POINTER},
	${AKTENPLANID},
	${ERZEUGER},
	TO_DATE(${ERZEUGUNGSDATUM}, 'DD.MM.YYYY hh24:mi:ss'),
	${AENDERER},
	TO_DATE(${AENDERUNGSDATUM}, 'DD.MM.YYYY hh24:mi:ss'),
	${DOKSTATUS},
	${PRODUCER},
	${DOKUMENTNAME}
	)

83-b87b34da-c4b2-46dc-aaff-1a1c22f44ea1-.name: PerTim_PepPly_TE_LU_Sql_10_30126_DbRdr
83-b87b34da-c4b2-46dc-aaff-1a1c22f44ea1-.file:
SELECT 
	'PERSONALNUMMER' AS PERSONALNUMMER,
	'IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN' AS IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN,
	'DATUM' AS DATUM,
	'UNIQUEIDENTIFIER' AS MYUID
FROM DUAL
UNION
SELECT 
	PERSONALNUMMER AS PERSONALNUMMER,
	TO_CHAR (IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN) AS IST_ZEIT_IN_SEKUNDEN,
	TO_CHAR (DATUM,'DD.MM.YYYY') AS DATUM,
	PERSONALNUMMER || '' AS MYUID
FROM MIS.V_HEATINFORMATIK_TEST
ORDER BY PERSONALNUMMER DESC

83-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.name: SrvLog_MirOsm_PR_LU_Xml_10_90083_DbRdr
83-19540655-2c11-4640-8016-d5d94c0a7dd9-.file:
SELECT 
	E.ID AS EVENT_ID,
	E.DATE_CREATED AS EVENT_DATE_CREATED,
	E.NAME AS EVENT_NAME, 
	E.EVENT_LEVEL AS EVENT_EVENT_LEVEL, 
	E.OUTCOME AS EVENT_OUTCOME, 
	E.ATTRIBUTES AS EVENT_ATTRIBUTES, 
	E.USER_ID AS EVENT_USER_ID, 
	E.IP_ADDRESS AS EVENT_IP_ADDRESS, 
	E.SERVER_ID AS EVENT_SERVER_ID,
	P.USERNAME AS PERSON_USERNAME
FROM EVENT E LEFT JOIN PERSON P ON E.USER_ID = P.ID WHERE E.SENT IS NULL AND E.NAME NOT LIKE 'Data Pruner'
